ith K-Means-LSTM has a higher accuracy with an\nRMSE of 601.20 whereas the SEIR model with an RMSE of 3615.83.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Jun 2020 01:42:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-30"}
