 invasion of\naqueous phases, such as fracture fluid and hazardous wastes, are affected by\nvug porosity but not their distribution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Jun 2020 15:03:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-30"}
